headline: RPC Expands Permian Reach With $245M Pintail Acquisition
summary: RES strengthens its Permian Basin footprint with the $245M acquisition of Pintail Completions, adding a leading wireline service provider to its oilfield services portfolio.

headline: ConocoPhillips Eyes $1B Sale of Oklahoma Oil & Gas Assets
summary: COP is evaluating the sale of Oklahoma assets inherited from Marathon Oil, aiming to raise $2 billion from non-core divestitures to sharpen its focus on key U.S. basins.
